<HEADLINE>
FOXY LADIES  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of ``HIGH STYLE AND MORE.''
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, see end of text. 
 &HT;    
 (Three color slides are available.) 
 From WWD 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
 &HT;    NEW YORK _ Young and sexy with a dash of ladylike polish _
that's the spirit this season at both Chloe and Valentino.
 &HT;    For Chloe, Stella McCartney featured cool denim pants and skirts
paired with studded blouses or sheer tops over tiny bras decorated
with the phrase ``forget me not.''
 &HT;    Valentino, on the other hand, opted for more refined ladylike
looks such as long, flowing gowns with daring slits and a duster
coat with a matching skirt.
 &HT;    
 &HT;     c.2000 Fairchild Publications 
