<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AIRLINES' WEB SITE FOR TICKETS COULD BE ABUSED, CRITICS WARN
 &HT;    With INTERNET-DATA. Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial
categories.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
