<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-20 17:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7961 &Cx1f; tad-z
u v BC-SPOT-BJT21-COXUPDATE     07-20 3534
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SPOT-BJT21-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 UPDATE &HT;    UPDATE
 &HT;    CoxNet Cox News Service budget
 &HT;    FOR FRIDAY, July 21, 2000
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   For questions, please call 404-526-5456.
