<HEADER>
A7990 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-ELIMINATE-BRITAIN-POL     07-20 0033
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-BRITAIN-POLITICS-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   BRITAIN-POLITICS (London) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service, June 20.
</P>
</TEXT>
