   LUCENT_Chart -- tk -- (BC-LUCENT-EARNINGS-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Lucent earnings chart.
</P>
<P>
   MONEY_Credit history -- 2 x 4 3/4 -- (BC-MONEY-ART-BOS)
</P>
<P>
   Taking your financial history coming up with a "credit score"
between 300 and 900.
</P>
