   PEACE-TALKS (Washington) _ The Middle East peace summit enters a
10th day minus President Clinton, who announced before leaving for
an international conference in Japan that Palestinian leader Yasser
Arafat and Israeli Prime Minister Ehud Barak would remain at Camp
David. By GREG McDONALD.
