   POLITICAL NEWS (``p'' category)
</P>
<P>
   GORE (San Antonio) _ Vice President Al Gore takes his Democratic
presidential campaign into his opponent's state, accusing Texas
Gov. George W. Bush of putting tax cuts ahead of public needs. By
PATTY REINERT.
