<P>
   CAMPAIGN-FINANCE (Washington) _ Rep. Tom DeLay, R-Texas, plans
to argue for abolition of all limits on campaign contributions and
will plead with Republican allies to fight any further progress by
campaign finance reformers. ``Unfettered political speech, along
with the right to bear arms, is the most certain means we possess
of protecting the rest of our freedoms,'' DeLay says in remarks
prepared for delivery at a Washington policy institute. By LETITIA
STEIN.
</P>
