</P>
<P>
   G8-SUMMIT (Okinawa City, Japan) _ President Clinton is scheduled
to speak Friday at an Okinawa peace park and to meet with President
Vladimir Putin of Russia. Clinton was greeted by anti-American
protesters as he arrived for the Group of Eight economic
conference. By DAVID IVANOVICH.
</P>
